{
  "stem": "33.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 88,
      "text": "And I'm saying it was unfortunate, because he instantly saw that the only possibility to hide would be in a capital city of Budapest-- that we will never be able to hide in a small town, because everybody knows us.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 89,
      "text": "But unfortunately, traveling was not possible for Jews anymore.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 90,
      "text": "But probably we could have even managed that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 91,
      "text": "But they took-- the Germans, the Nazis, took 80 Jewish adult men as hostages in my town.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 92,
      "text": "And my father was one of them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 93,
      "text": "They locked them up in a house that belonged to a Jewish family.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 94,
      "text": "And they evacuated them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 95,
      "text": "And every single day, the Gestapo, the German Secret Police, would go in there, and they would threaten the hostages.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 96,
      "text": "That if any of the family tried to hide or escape, they would shoot the hostage immediately.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 97,
      "text": "They did make sure, through the Hungarian police, that the family-- we the family-- knew about this threat.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 98,
      "text": "At that time, in the same block where we lived, there was a Jewish hospital that was evacuated.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 99,
      "text": "And they brought an army-- a Hungarian army hospital in these-- instead of this Jewish hospital.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 100,
      "text": "And the doctors who came with this hospital, with the army, they were quartered in our street.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we got, at the beginning, we got two Hungarian doctors who where in the army.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then one of them moved somewhere else.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we had one.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "These people came from the front.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they knew that they lost the war.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they saw all terrible things that happened.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they really, in their minds, they just couldn't understand all this persecution and that-- what was going on.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because they knew that it's the end.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they're losing the war anyway.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
